/*
 * Function: Set1Dot
 * Used to set the color of the dot
 * Called when a new message arrives
 * Parameters: int dotcode:
 *   - 0 == Dot1 off
 *   - 1 == Dot1 on
 *   - 2 == Dot2 off
 *   - 3 == Dot2 on
 */
